title: The Recruit - S02E07
description:
The Recruit - S02E07

Teamwork is tested as seven men remain in the running for their dream prize: an AFL contract. Paul Licuria pops in to the training session while the boys are pushed to their limits. It's a pressure test at the racetrack as Matt races to become king of The Pits and try for two-time captaincy, and Daniel leaves the team unimpressed with his lack of effort around his food. There's no game this week but the recruits puzzle their way through a Fitbit Challenge and one of the favourites makes a shock delist decision.
